The original of this file was created by the user Shonosh at Blenderartists.org. https://blenderartists.org/t/uv-islands-to-hard-edges/643935

I have just changed it slightly so it works with Blender 2.80.

I updated the version number, removed a description that was causing an error, and added a check to see if anything was selected.

The instalation is as any other blender add-on.
